'''水蛛'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|''Argyroneta aquatica''}}），又名'''潜水钟蜘蛛'''，为[[叶蛛科|叶蛛科]]'''水蛛属'''的[[单型|唯一一种蜘蛛]]。分布于[[欧洲|欧洲]]以及[[中国大陆|中国大陆]]的[[内蒙古|内蒙古]]、[[吉林|吉林]]等地，常栖息于淡水中，是唯一一种完全生活在水中的蜘蛛。该物种的模式产地在欧洲<ref name='id14006'>{{cite web| url =http://www.bioinfo.cn/db05/BjdwSpecies.php?action=view&id=14006| title =水蛛| work =《中国动物物种编目数据库》| publisher =中国科学院微生物研究所| author =中国科学院动物研究所| accessdate =2009-04-28| deadurl =yes| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20160305031649/http://www.bioinfo.cn/db05/BjdwSpecies.php?action=view&id=14006| archivedate =2016-03-05}}</ref>。其身長可達15公分，雄性體型比雌性大。

==习性==
[[File:Argyroneta_Aquatica.jpg|thumb]]

水蛛是一种完全生活在水下的蜘蛛，它们在水下栖息、捕食、交配、产卵，它们一般仅在需要补充氧气的时候浮上水面，偶尔也会带着猎物浮上水面<ref name=Thorp2015>{{cite book | editor1=Thorp, J.H. | editor2=D.C. Rogers |year=2015 | title=Thorp and Covich's Freshwater Invertebrates: Ecology and General Biology | publisher=Elsevier | pages=602–608 | volume=1 | edition=4 | isbn=978-0-12-385026-3 }}</ref><ref name=Hillyard2007>{{cite book | author=Hillyard, P.D. |year=2007 | title=The Private Life of Spiders | publisher=New Holland | pages=41–43 | isbn=978-0-69115-003-1 }}</ref><ref name=BAS>{{cite web | title=Argyroneta aquatica (Araneae) | url=http://srs.britishspiders.org.uk/portal.php/p/Summary/s/Argyroneta+aquatica | website=British Arachnological Society | accessdate=12 April 2018 | archive-date=2020-02-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200223170314/http://srs.britishspiders.org.uk/portal.php/p/Summary/s/Argyroneta+aquatica | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Schutz2007>{{Cite journal |author1=Schütz, D. |author2=M. Taborsky | author3=T. Drapela |date=2007 |title=Air bells of water spiders are an extended phenotype modified in response to gas composition | journal=J Exp Zool a Ecol Genet Physiol. |volume=307 | issue=10 |pages=549–555 |doi=10.1002/jez.410 |pmid=17674350 }}</ref>。它们在水面上获得氧气后，会将气泡存储在腹部和腿上疏水性的毛发间，这时候腹部看起来就像是镀了一层银一般<ref name="Schütz 2003"/>。人工饲养的水蛛平均寿命为两年。<ref name="Schütz 2003">{{cite journal|author1=Schütz, D. |author2=Taborsky, M. |title=Adaptations to an aquatic life may be responsible for the reversed sexual size dimorphism in the water spider, ''Argyroneta aquatica'' |journal=Evolutionary Ecology Research |year=2003 |volume=5 |issue=1 |pages=105–117 |url=http://www.zoology.unibe.ch/behav/pdf_files/Schuetz_EvolEcolRes03.pdf |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081216214632/http://www.zoology.unibe.ch/behav/pdf_files/Schuetz_EvolEcolRes03.pdf |archivedate=2008-12-16 }}</ref>

它们生活在英国、欧洲大陆和北亚<ref name=SpidersEurope>{{cite web | year=2013 | title=Argyroneta aquatica (Clerck, 1757) | url=https://araneae.unibe.ch/data/201 | website=Araneae – Spiders of Europe | accessdate=12 April 2018 }}{{Dead link|date=2020年7月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>干净的淡水中湖泊、池塘及流速缓慢的溪流中<ref name=BAS/><ref>{{cite web | author=Filoramo, R. | year=2012 | title=Argyroneta aquatica | url=http://animaldiversity.org/accounts/Argyroneta_aquatica/ | website=Animal Diversity Web | accessdate=12 April 2018 | archive-date=2020-09-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200906042731/https://animaldiversity.org/accounts/Argyroneta_aquatica/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>，日本存在水蛛的一个亚种''[[日本水蛛|A. a. japonica]]''<ref>{{Cite journal |author=Ono, H. |date=2002 |title=New and Remarkable Spiders of the Families Liphistiidae, Argyronetidae, Pisauridae, Theridiidae and Araneidae (Arachnida) from Japan |journal=Bulletin of the National Museum of Nature and Science Tokyo (A) |volume=28 |issue=1 |pages=51–60 |doi=10.1016/j.crvi.2018.02.002  |pmid=29530733 |url=http://prodinra.inra.fr/ft/7DA2A7D9-D687-4289-A596-B96F743B48B5 }}</ref>。它们在水面上获得氧气后，会将气泡存储在腹部和腿上疏水性的毛发间，这时候腹部看起来就像是镀了一层银一般<ref name="Schütz 2003"/>。

雄蛛比雌蛛大30%，长{{convert|10-15|mm|in|abbr=on}}，雌蛛长{{convert|8-12|mm|in|abbr=on}}<ref name=DanmarksEdderkopper>{{cite web | title=Argyroneta aquatica (Clerck 1758) (Water spider) | url=http://danmarks-edderkopper.dk/species-description?taxon=Argyroneta%20aquatica | website=danmarks-edderkopper.dk | accessdate=14 September 2015 | archive-date=2018-01-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180118122623/http://danmarks-edderkopper.dk/species-description?taxon=Argyroneta%20aquatica | dead-url=no }}</ref>。这种两性异形特征在蜘蛛中也是很罕见，一般都是雌蛛比雄蛛大。这可能是由于更活跃的雄蛛需要更大的力量来抵抗水中的压力。<ref name="Schütz 2003" />

它们以水中的昆虫和甲壳动物为食，常见的食物包括孑孓和[[水蚤|水蚤]]<ref name="Seymour 2011">{{Cite journal |last = Seymour |first=R. S. |last2=Hetz |first2=S. K. | title=The diving bell and the spider: the physical gill of ''Argyroneta aquatica'' | journal= J. Exp. Biol. |volume=214 |issue=13 | year = 2011 |pages =2175–2181 |doi=10.1242/jeb.056093 |pmid=21653811 }}</ref>。它们的天敌则是蛙类和鱼类。<ref name="Water Spider">{{cite web |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131111020107/https://www.buzzle.com/articles/water-spider.html |title=Water Spider |author=Chandramita Bora}}</ref>

